    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>,<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> pomegranate molasses </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>mustard ketchup </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> brown sugar </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 25ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[40ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [50ml]</span><strong> cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up –<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>Kansas-style BBQ sauce</strong></p>",
