    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cheesy macaroni</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (use individual ones for fancy presentation!) and top with the <strong>remaining grated cheddar</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 15 min or until bubbling and golden – this is<strong> the daddy</strong> <strong>mac 'n' cheese</strong></p><p>Tip: The cheese sauce will thicken in the oven!</p>",
