    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, slice the <strong>Kansas-style BBQ chicken </strong>on a clean chopping board</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and chop into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced Kansas-style BBQ chicken</strong> with <strong>the daddy mac 'n' cheese</strong> and <strong>lettuce wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Add a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> to the <strong>lettuce wedges </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
